snippet.title: Angry Birds Match - Teaser trailer #3
snippet.description:
Angry Birds Match - the cutest puzzle game ever is here! 

The pigs are trying their hardest to ruin the Hatchlings’ party, but nothing can stop these little guys! Match the toys, stars, stuff and things to collect everything your Hatchlings ask for!


▶︎ Play Angry Birds Match NOW:
http://rov.io/PlayMatch_yt
